    == Installation

    The project requires Python 3.12 and uses #link("https://docs.astral.sh/uv/")[uv] for dependency management. The `reeds_shepp` dependency is vendored under `deps/pyReedsShepp` and built automatically on install.

    ```sh
    git clone <repo-url>
    cd valet

    # create a virtual environment and install all dependencies
    uv sync
    ```

    In addition to the dependencies installed by `uv`, `deps/pyReedsShepp` has an additional C dependency through #link("https://www.boost.org/")[`boost`]. See `README.md` for additional installation instructions.

    == Usage

    Run the simulator with:

    ```sh
    uv run runsim [bot_type] [options]
    ```

    `bot_type` is one of `point`, `diff`, `car`, `trailer` (default: `diff`).

